channel.title: I need an answer, this is pissing me off. [no-ip shit]
channel.description:
Alright. Well yeah I like coding servers, clients, w/e, but i've never ACTUALLY got to have the fun of hosting a server ! I used to! I had 200 players online ! But randomly, my no-ip stopped working? I've tried so much ip's, from .serve-beer, servegame.com, no-ip.info, no-ip.biz, no-ip.org! EVERYTHING, Everyone used to be able to connect, not anymore. Nobody can connect.
[IMG]http://i33.tinypic.com/33bhd1k.png[/img] Those are my two ports I have for my server, none of them work.
